{
  "stem": "27409.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The local populations, they let us in the room with them in their-- [INAUDIBLE] [NON-ENGLISH], a room in their house, which I had to pay.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We started living there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were not permitted [INAUDIBLE] to leave the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We had three or four soldiers which were permanently there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the soldiers which looted us were mostly from the prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I was called to the prisoner of war camp 1, because I had the list of the hundred which came there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the Praetor, that was remain in highest authority in Shargorod, wanted to see me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I came there with Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Hagar.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I learned his son who was sent there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And he asked me--he wanted say to make the list of the Jews age, everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I was there as student, written, or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We returned home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was night, a bitter night, and cold and the snow is this-- that became as a [INAUDIBLE] from the [NON-ENGLISH], but it left.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Nobody was on the way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Only we had animals [INAUDIBLE] and this, but nobody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We came back and we started preparing for the worse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "In the-- in Shargorod, there were Jews from south and Bukovina had organized a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It was-- the head was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], a local lawyer, which arranged with the Romanian authority, except with-- the Praetor was a beast, inhuman [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I remember, his name, Denvulik, Dan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "His hobby was beating Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He went just beating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And they had the Germans and Germany-- small, got his own [INAUDIBLE], so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But they were not active.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They were most in the region against from a Communist soul-searching.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Because with the Jews, you could speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "They were the only from Bukovina that could speak German.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
